title: Patch 6.3 is live!
body:
Hi Everyone,

6.3 is now live on Oceania and we are here and waiting to respond to any first day patch issues you may encounter. If you do encounter any bugs after patching, please post them here for our team to investigate.

Cheers!
-Mindstar

replies.body: sometimes when i got to my champion page and match history, its the look from like late season 4-early season 5? whats going on with this. theres no champion mastery apparently and my match history looks really old so does the champion page obviously as well.

With patch 6.3 the new ad item came out ( Duskblade of Draktharr )

Question - Why does this passive trigger on a vessel ( illaoi's E ) ? 

does it work like illaoi's ult where if there is a vessel you gain an extra tentacle ?
The new item works well with Zed{{champion:238}} {{item:3147}}
haha bro the new item was almost built just for zed, double ult in one go

Hey man,

I believe Vessels are counted as a class of champions for spell interactions. Thats why Illaoi's ult gives a tentacle for a vessel. Therefore Duskblade would proc on a Vessel too.
that makes sense i suppose, thanks for explaining
